{"tid":338401,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPod nano, iPod shuffle官方正式停售 蘋果音樂專用播放機絕跡","createTime":"2017-07-28T07:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T14:23:31.000Z","uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82f9898c7635fcc67ed520a12ee23c62aff6d55b","tid":338401,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/8943041/55313315.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_asset%2Ffile%2F8943041%2F55313315.jpg&h=d2734314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果在今日終於將音樂播放機iPod nano與iPod shuffle從Apple Store網上商店正式下架，同時間有關iPod nano與iPod shuffle的介紹頁面也完全刪去。除了是兩個產品的終結，亦代表蘋果音樂專門播放機完全絕跡，iPod系列只剩下iPod touch第6代，這部可以上網玩App又可聽歌的「播放器」。同時間亦代表Steve Jobs令蘋果起死回生的iPod系列，只剩下iPod touch這個「孤兒仔」。<br />\n<br />\n第一部iPod shuffle與iPod nano分別在2005年1月與9月推出，當時Steve Jobs首次利用到快閃記憶體作為音樂播放器的儲存裝置，輕巧細小，Steve Jobs在發佈會中從牛仔褲袋中掏出iPod nano的一幕可謂經典。這兩部專門播放音樂的隨身機，曾經引起MP3機熱潮。可惜，現在已經沒有人記得起甚麼叫「音樂播放機」，除了一些只有迎合發燒友市場的極高階的機種外，平民MP3機都整合到智能電話之上。如果你突然想保留呢段歷史，就要看看各大電器鋪還有沒有存貨了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/snap3868-768x429.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Fsnap3868-768x429.png&h=89a176be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7bf4924ea9551de6a66688758f65a350427f39","tid":338401,"uid":22658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"曾經我都有部shuffle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家仲有部classic係到封塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3446827c8f4e87b6f4cc85dc5afd6722a0c792f","tid":338401,"uid":12537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:32:19.000Z","msg":"記得iPod Nano可以加錶帶用<br />\n跟住攞咗部gen1去apple store換<br />\n但其實gen1白色好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e69dde086102a75f5dde2643de71e3a4de23f2f","tid":338401,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:35:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得iPod Nano可以加錶帶用<br />\n跟住攞咗部gen1去apple store換<br />\n但其實gen1白色好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nnano6 我仲係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63c1af1340652c7c8b7771d2c241b8fce2a90bf","tid":338401,"uid":131033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾經我都有部shuffle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家仲有部classic係到封塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我部ipod classic都放左係屋企封塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21625309081bfd83bd9d5519e796f28646c3f60","tid":338401,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:43:58.000Z","msg":"iPod出ge聲其實唔靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔支援FLAC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21783ea2f68ea52c660379275f81cb8c36608bf7","tid":338401,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/8943041/55313315.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_asset%2Ffile%2F8943041%2F55313315.jpg&h=d2734314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果在今日終於將音樂播放機iPod nano與iPod shuffle從Apple Store網上商店正式下架，同時間有關iPo